==Description==
The '''Heat Rock''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Heat Rock has a value of 2 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Heat Rock appears in the Underground as a 3x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:HeatRockMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Heat Rocks can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

